Package org.neo4j.internal.index.label

Class EmptyingRelationshipTypeScanStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.index.label.EmptyingRelationshipTypeScanStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RelationshipTypeScanStore, TokenScanStore, ConsistencyCheckable, Lifecycle
    public final class EmptyingRelationshipTypeScanStore
extends Object
implements RelationshipTypeScanStore
    This is an almost no-op relationship type scan store and is used in place of the real implementation when rtss is turned OFF. It does one thing and that is delete any rtss file that exists during startup. In this way we make sure that when rtss is turned back ON again it will be rebuilt. We need to do this because we don't know if rtss missed any updates while it was turned OFF.
